{"tid":618580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵列車往利東站途中　乘客手機冒煙急疏散","createTime":"2018-04-06T02:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T17:51:41.000Z","uid":176442,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab6a4896d6a6d701765cbeb7c91d582234adf6f","tid":618580,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180406/bkn-20180406095714725-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180406%2Fbkn-20180406095714725-0406_00822_001.html&d=BqGjCycW4fN3prVCEleS%2FttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fca666b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180406/bkn-20180406095714725-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"14e470d743711348819e0bf4ca3b3a891e86c317","tid":618580,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"港鐵列車發生乘客手機冒煙意外。早上9時02分，南港島線一列由海怡半島站開往利東站的列車，在行駛途中，一名乘客的手機突然冒煙，嚇得立即將手機拋下，另一名乘客見狀，從車廂取出滅火筒噴射。當列車抵達後，月台上的職員，立即安排乘客疏散，幸有驚無險，乘客並改搭下一班列車繼續行程。肇事列車則駛返黃竹坑車廠檢查，警方及消防員到車廠了解。"},{"pid":"310818ea2a35553929ce6c46ef9446c84b6ab394","tid":618580,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"估下係咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a506aec15b9aa0291b28b934628501c8ed78979","tid":618580,"uid":50595,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:32:18.000Z","msg":"一定係iphone"},{"pid":"a7dab3fdfe9e48331f76063cc33394ef8d6514f6","tid":618580,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"三叔？"},{"pid":"85d0485d59fdbeea24c946b74f6b3060ab02521f","tid":618580,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:55:27.000Z","msg":"小米"},{"pid":"9cb2146ddc3783f737294c3916ada13edc002a3b","tid":618580,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T